    Proxy -->|"PostgreSQL/5432<br/>Optional TLS 1.2+<br/>Username/Password (Secret)"| PostgreSQL
    Controller -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>Cluster-internal<br/>Bearer Token (optional)"| Proxy
    Controller -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS<br/>SA Token"| K8sAPI
    K8sAPI -->|"Watch notifications<br/>HTTP/2 TLS<br/>SA Token"| Controller
    Prometheus -->|"HTTPS/8443<br/>TLS (self-signed)<br/>Bearer Token"| Controller
    StorageInit -->|"HTTP/8080<br/>No Auth"| Proxy
    StorageInit -->|"HTTPS/443<br/>TLS 1.2+<br/>Provider Credentials"| ModelStorage

